text: Bombayla Devi Laishram is an Indian archer. She was born on 22 February 1985. Laishram competed at the 2008 Summer Olympics, 2012 Summer Olympics, and the 2016 Summer Olympics.Bombayla DeviLaishram Bombayla DEVI == References == Category:Living people Category:1985 births Category:Indian archers Category:Olympians for India
